## ğŸ“± Commands

### `/embed "Your Title"`
**Simple Embed Builder** (3 fields - **GUARANTEED** to work)

| Field | Description | Required |
|-------|-------------|----------|
| **Description** | Main embed text (paragraph) | âŒ No |
| **Color** | HEX color (`#FAD5A5` default) | âŒ No |
| **Image URL** | Direct image link | âŒ No |

**Example:** `/embed "Welcome to Sumo!"`

---

### `/embed_pro "Your Title"`
**Advanced Embed Builder** (5 fields - **Professional**)

| Field | Description | Required |
|-------|-------------|----------|
| **Description** | Main embed text | âŒ No |
| **Color** | HEX color (`#FAD5A5` default) | âŒ No |
| **Image URL** | Main embed image | âŒ No |
| **Thumbnail URL** | Small side image | âŒ No |
| **Footer** | Bottom text | âŒ No |

**Example:** `/embed_pro "Server Rules"`

---

### `/embed_preview`
**Usage Guide** - Shows all commands + external embed builder link

Simple: /embed "Title"
Pro: /embed_pro "Title"
Advanced: https://glitchii.github.io/embedbuilder/

